description: ZignSec AB provides information technology solutions. The company is headquartered in Solna, Stockholm. The company went IPO on 2019-10-21. Its product, ZignSec, is an identity service cloud platform for the online customer verification. The platform provides users with a suite of products, such as electronic identities, online ID scanning, register checks, real-time payments, phone number validation, banking API (application programming interface) and income analysis, among others, by focusing on identify the real person behind every user or transaction. The Company’s solutions are dedicated to all businesses where KYC (know your customers) and AML (anti money laundering)-regulations exists such as financial services, i-gaming and e-health.
